    <item>
      <title>苏丹战争可能引发 2500 万人面临饥饿危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/war-in-sudan-risks-sparking-hunger-crisis-for-25-million-people</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界粮食计划署执行主任辛迪·麦凯恩表示，苏丹战争使苏丹、南苏丹和乍得 2500 万人的粮食安全面临风险，成为全球最大的饥饿危机，呼吁畅通无阻地提供援助并提供更多资金来帮助社区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/war-in-sudan-risks-sparking-hunger-crisis-for-25-million-people</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 06:57:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币价格创历史新高后波动性加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/bitcoin-btc-retreats-after-record-breaking-run-that-topped-69-000</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币在创下两年多以来的首个记录后出现大幅波动，交易员评估了最近推出的交易所交易基金的需求是否能够维持该代币的涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/bitcoin-btc-retreats-after-record-breaking-run-that-topped-69-000</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 03:07:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特选择提高亚洲油价后油价小幅走高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯出人意料地向亚洲买家提高了主要级别的价格，投资者等待美联储有关美国货币政策的线索，油价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 23:24:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储作证前股市小幅走高：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔发表证词之前，美国股指期货和欧洲合约小幅上涨。在官员宣布雄心勃勃的 5% 增长目标后，投资者还关注中国的政策会议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 22:46:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度加强打击影子银行，JM Financial 暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/india-bars-jm-financial-from-lending-against-shares-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行禁止 JM Financial Ltd. 子公司发放股票和债券贷款，加上最近采取的抑制投机性投资的监管举措，导致 JM Financial Ltd. 在孟买股价暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/india-bars-jm-financial-from-lending-against-shares-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 14:29:00 GMT</pubDate>
